{"tid":292269,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"【快的跪低】即日起刪去85折選項 強調從不以此作招徠","createTime":"2017-06-21T08:32:30.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-21T08:38:31.000Z","uid":17738,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"fae95ed5e5fd3bd48dbd3879009115ed02416ab8","tid":292269,"uid":17738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-21T08:32:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.appledaily.com.hk/images/e-paper/20170621/large/1498028111_844d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.appledaily.com.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170621%2Flarge%2F1498028111_844d.jpg&h=fa5f11fa&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n近日電召車應用程式「快的打車」忽然顯示「85折」選項，變相提供折扣吸客，可能違法。快的今發表聲明，指備註顯示選項為用戶熱門搜尋字眼，為免誤會，即日起刪去「85折」標籤。<br />\n<br />\n快的聲明指，應用程式的「備註」會自動顯示乘客常用搜尋字眼，給予乘客多種選擇，按搜尋熱度於頁面自動顯示。<br />\n<br />\n對於有報導指，香港的士近日加價導致乘客更多主動要求85折，快的不排除這是構成該系統發現「85折」為常用字的原因。快的強調，從不以「85折」作招徠，相反更鼓勵乘客在繁忙時段或天氣不穩定時適量添加小費。<br />\n<br />\n為免進一步構成誤會，快的決定由即日起鏟除「備註」內「＋85折」標籤，但乘客未來也可在「備註」內手動輸入其他請求，如「5人車」、「西隧」、「綠的」等等。<br />\n<br />\n運輸署昨指，按《道路交通（公共服務車輛）規例》第40條訂明的「兜客」行為，若的士司機、其代表或看來是代表該司機行事的人主動提供優惠或車費折扣作招徠，誘使乘客使用其車輛；不論透過手機應用程式、電話或其他方式，已屬「兜客」行為，若無合理辯解，即屬違法。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=56857399&amp;category_guid=7015342&amp;category=instant&amp;issue=20170621\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D56857399%26category_guid%3D7015342%26category%3Dinstant%26issue%3D20170621&d=JCnWpoNFTYXb1hSje%2B7cQOargVTjPUnXFlgjsLUvQ6w%3D&h=a9272630\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D56857399%26category_guid%3D7015342%26category%3Dinstant%26issue%3D20170621&h=77453744\" target=\"_blank\">http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=56857399&amp;category_guid=7015342&amp;category=instant&amp;issue=20170621</a>"},{"pid":"d92af82ecb14ac61bb8a0ded5b87e9c3f6d66fa2","tid":292269,"uid":54502,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-21T08:35:59.000Z","msg":"冇折我洗撚用你呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"10e28e6ef63d9bbf3a9b089d86d597c736c0d5b0","tid":292269,"uid":21423,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-21T08:38:31.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}